snippet.title: Fire Emblem Fates: V.O.W Edition "The Vanished Queen" All Cutscenes
snippet.description:
This is all the cutscenes for Beatrice's Paralogue chapter. Major spoilers to those who want to experience it for themselves!

Voices used:
ElevenLabs - Yasuo/Hilde (https://beta.elevenlabs.io/speech-synthesis)
Iroryu - Yasuo (Liam O' Brian)
Beatrice - Hilde SCVI (Julie Ann Taylor)
Kara - Female Veteran Knight SCVI

Music used:
DMC3 - Total Result
Fire Emblem Awakening music
Kevin Kiner - Death of a Master

Link to VOW Edition discord:
https://discord.com/invite/H5eQSSY2hp
